    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_13_22293-22320",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "22293-22320",
      "markText": "绝欺压，可使有限的恩惠，真正施及于灾民，不致有名无实。",
      "totalCount": 2142,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=22293&rangeEnd=22320",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=22293&rangeEnd=22320"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_14_32794-32830",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "32794-32830",
      "markText": "至于宋代的水利灌溉，在政府方面虽颇为注重，但灌溉事业的功绩，也不如前代。",
      "totalCount": 2142,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=32794&rangeEnd=32830",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=32794&rangeEnd=32830"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_12_6083-6095",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6083-6095",
      "markText": "“洪武三年，夏，久不雨。",
      "totalCount": 2102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6083&rangeEnd=6095",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6083&rangeEnd=6095"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_14_43566-43611",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "43566-43611",
      "markText": "明初正当元末大乱之后，“山东、河南多是无人之地，洪武中诏有能开垦者，即为己业，永不起科。”",
      "totalCount": 2077,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=43566&rangeEnd=43611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=43566&rangeEnd=43611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_12_6268-6308",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6268-6308",
      "markText": "如晋代，旱则祈雨大雩，有舞僮八佾，计六十四人，都穿玄服、持羽翳而歌《云汉》之诗。",
      "totalCount": 2012,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6268&rangeEnd=6308",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6268&rangeEnd=6308"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_8_4760-4819",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4760-4819",
      "markText": "据过去官方的和半官方的统计材料，我国农村人口死亡率约为千分之二十五至二十六，即平均每年每千人中约死二十五人至二十六人。",
      "totalCount": 1991,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4760&rangeEnd=4819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4760&rangeEnd=4819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_14_34602-34651",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "34602-34651",
      "markText": "三为甘肃靖远的黄河堰，一望无边际，较大的渠，有汉伯渠、胡渠、御史渠，每渠又各有支渠，灌溉田地颇多。",
      "totalCount": 1984,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=34602&rangeEnd=34651",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=34602&rangeEnd=34651"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_6_8071-8115",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8071-8115",
      "markText": "东晋之后，南北朝割据，百六十九年中，水、旱、蝗螟、地震、霜雹、疫疠等灾害共达三百十五次。",
      "totalCount": 1966,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8071&rangeEnd=8115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8071&rangeEnd=8115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_8_4439-4493",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4439-4493",
      "markText": "这大量流移的受灾人口，虽然成群结队，相继离村，但流徙到别的州郡以后，求食很困难，甚至有被地方官吏下令捕逐的。",
      "totalCount": 1966,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4439&rangeEnd=4493",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4439&rangeEnd=4493"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_13_22338-22378",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "22338-22378",
      "markText": "严检查，则可以戢暴诘奸，户口也要调查详实，审查便利，粮食的供需，也就较易调节了。",
      "totalCount": 1966,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=22338&rangeEnd=22378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=22338&rangeEnd=22378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_13_42042-42064",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "42042-42064",
      "markText": "自东汉以后，才渐渐注意广泛的医治和公共防疫。",
      "totalCount": 1941,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300154826&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=42042&rangeEnd=42064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a032de0813aba2fag016fb6?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=42042&rangeEnd=42064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300154826_8_27309-27350",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "27309-27350",
      "markText": "灾荒的延长，自然会消磨民族内在的力量，内力不充，外力就得以侵入，这是很平常的道理。",
